SCYX Recent publication provided evidence that application of Caspofungin during Apergillus fumigatus growth mutates the fungus into a new species thats echinocandin resistant The experiment used fks1 genes that had no mutations a clean baseline sample This was traced to stress within the lipid This is one more reason to use ibrexafungerp or something else CD101 rezafungin is echinocandin class its a reformulated long acting echinocandin mbioasmorgcontent103e
